msgstr "这是基于您当前已保存规则生成的 nftables 配置文件。"

msgid "this shows the ACTUAL rules and routing policies currently active in the linux kernel."
msgstr "这里展示的是当前 Linux 内核中真正生效的规则、策略和路由。"

